name: lets keep it real 1.0
description: nature shots glitching because a simulation of real nature might be the only option to enjoy planet earth if we dont start taking fckn care of it. The lets keep it real connection is a daily reminder that nature is still out there and its our responsibility to find ways to save it. NFTs and art can help. 20% of the proceeds will go to the non profit one tree planted, which plants 1 tree per $1 donated, a certificate will be sent to the owner. Art is power, art can save our world.
